<!---------------------------->
<table cellpadding=2 cellspacing=2>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Recommended Level<br>for starting quest:</b></td><td valign="bottom"> 30<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Starting zone:</b></td><td valign="top"> The Overthere<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Additional zones:</b></td><td valign="top"> --<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Starting NPC:</b></td><td valign="top"> Captain Rottgrime<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Reward:</b></td><td valign="top"> Guard of the Marines<br><br></td></tr>
</table>

It should be noted that the real reward for this quest is a faction increase with Venril Sathir so that you can obtain the hammer which will port you to the Outpost in the Overthere.<br>
<br>
Captain Rottgrime asks you to kill Sarnaks (specifically berserkers) and return to him 4 of their war braids.  For every four you hand him, you will receive the Guard of the Marines (a crappy shield), faction, and a little bit of money.<br>
<br>
Captain Rottgrime says, 'Great job marine!! Word of your heroics shall be passed on to the Admiral. If you don't have a shield then take one, if you do then get back to the frontlines. There is no time for R n' R!! Move it marine!! Or you'll be pushing Danak till the cockatrice crow!!'<br>
<br>
The Sarnak Berserkers are found wandering throughout the higher level areas of the zone (South and West walls) and in several camps of Sarnaks (such as the ruins near the mud pit).  The Berserkers will <b>always</b> drop one war brain (unless they have been disarmed or pickpocketed) and the war braid is NO DROP and not stackable.<br>
<br>
Completing this quest about 20 times should be enough to get your faction standing up to amiable so you can do the Worker Sledgemallet quest.  The experience received is also pretty good.<br>
<br>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP  <br>
AC: +8 Magic Resist: +10  <br>
Weight: 10.0 <br>
Classes: Ranger Shaman Cleric Paladin Shadowknight Bard Rogue Warrior  <br>
Races: All Races  <br>
Inventory Slot: Secondary<br>

